Class RuleSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khaledbakhit.api.rslib.ruleset.RuleSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RuleSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    RuleSet Object represents a RuleSet that contains many Rules and a default classification that help it classify DataSet cases.
